      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Dimensionless parameters (Reynolds number, flow coefficient) match between validation experiment and COU simulation to within 5%.",
      "rationale": "Flow coefficient phi and head coefficient psi computed for all five operating points. Maximum deviation between validation and COU operating conditions is 3.2% in phi and 4.1% in psi, within the 5% equivalency threshold. Geometric similarity confirmed by using identical CAD geometry for both validation and production runs."
    }
